HEADWORD: Clergyable
<hw>Cler"gy*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Entitled to, or
admitting, the benefit of clergy; <as>as, a <ex>clergyable</ex>
felony</as>.</def> <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
